						               													<description>Ojciec Mateusz: tajemnicze zagadki Sandomierza (Father Mateusz - mysterious riddles of Sandomierz) is board game inspired by popular tv series produced by TVP (polish television). In the game, players become detectives trying to outsmart the criminals, the action takes place in Sandomierz and helps them, of course, Father Mateusz.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In the game players encounter various obstacles, gather evidence, try to prevent criminals from stealing valuable treasures of Polish culture. To achieve this, they must go through the historical sites of the beautiful city Sandomierz. Players work together with the help of the Father Mateusz, who did not once indicate the appropriate solution.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;To each location in the beautifully illustrated game board is assigned a unique deck of cards with the evidence, traces, instructions, and... obstacles that hinder the detectives in traversing various places. Each player conducts its own investigation, he can help the other players but don't have to, because everyone is fighting for the same Investigation Points.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Box contains:&amp;#10;- Board with the panorama of Sandomierz&amp;#10;- 21 tokens&amp;#10;- 90 small cards including:&amp;#10;- 7 decks of locations&amp;#10;- 12 cards of Father Mateusz&amp;#10;- 12 cards of Doubt&amp;#10;- 30 cards of Story (4 investigations)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
